data.description: Spacious Corner Twin With Off-Street Parking Ready To Go! Located in the popular Burholme section of Northeast Philly, this brick porch front beauty has been beautifully maintained and tastefully updated by its current owner for your future comfort! The main floor features a formal living room, formal dining room, a bonus room, a full kitchen with tons of cabinet and counter space, granite countertops and tile backsplash. Upstairs are 3 very spacious bedrooms and a remodeled full bathroom. There is also a full basement and attic for storage. The outdoor space is abundant with your fully fenced-in rear and side yards featuring an above ground pool with a deck. Your 1 car detached garage provides off-street parking as well as additional storage. Other features include beautiful wood floors throughout, recently re-stained staircase, newer ceiling fans and light fixtures throughout and much more. Conveniently located within minutes of all public transportation, shopping, dining, and highway entrances. A True No-Brainer!!
